Description: Data manipulation for CMIP6 hydroclimatic data. The files are archived in the Federated Research Data Repository (FRDR; https://doi.org/10.20383/103.0829). The data set is described in Abdelmoaty et al., (2025 <https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-025-04396-z>)
